<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.3">
<l>ēṉatti ṉuruvāki nilamaṅkai yeḻilkoṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>vāṉatti lavarmuṟaiyāl makiḻntētti valaṅkoḷḷa</l>
<l>kāṉattiṉ kaṭalmallait talacayaṉat tuṟaikiṉṟa</l>
<l>ñāṉatti ṉoḷiyuruvai niṉaivāreṉ nāyakarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who contemplate the form of the light of knowledge which dwells</l>
<l>In Talacayaṉam at Mallai by the sea with forests, where those of heaven,</l>
<l>By turns circumambulate, being joyous praising him who as a boar</l>
<l>Took [up] the immensity of lady earth, they are my masters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
